transpositions.text:
^un jeu // {"headword":"jeu","category":"noun","gender":"masculine","cefrLevel":"A1"}
# Théorie des jeux

^une caractéristique // {"headword":"caractéristique","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"B2"}
## Caractéristiques

Quelles sont les caractéristiques de la théorie des jeux ?
^une décision // {"headword":"décision","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^un joueur // {"headword":"joueur","category":"noun","gender":"masculine","cefrLevel":"A2"}
^un humain // {"headword":"humain","category":"noun","gender":"masculine","cefrLevel":"A2"}
^rationnel // {"headword":"rationnel","category":"adjective","cefrLevel":"B2","gender":"masculine"}
Théorie de la décision, plusieurs joueurs, considère l'humain comme rationnel.

## Définitions

^une stratégie // {"headword":"stratégie","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"B1"}
### Stratégie

Qu'est-ce que la stratégie n'est pas ?
^une méthode // {"headword":"méthode","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"B1"}
Une méthode pour être le plus intelligent.

Qu'est-ce qu'une stratégie ?
^un plan // {"headword":"plan","category":"noun","gender":"masculine","cefrLevel":"A1"}
^un comportement // {"headword":"comportement","category":"noun","gender":"masculine","cefrLevel":"B2"}
^couvrir // {"headword":"couvrir","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^un cas // {"headword":"cas","category":"noun","gender":"masculine","cefrLevel":"A2"}
Un plan de comportement couvrant tous les cas.

^une somme // {"headword":"somme","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"A2"}
^nul // {"headword":"nul","category":"other","cefrLevel":"A2"}
### Jeu à somme nulle

Qu'est-ce qu'un jeu à somme nulle ?
^une situation // {"headword":"situation","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"A2"}
^un gain // {"headword":"gain","category":"noun","gender":"masculine","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^perdre // {"headword":"perdre","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"A2"}
^gagner // {"headword":"gagner","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"A1"}
^fixé // {"headword":"fixé","category":"adjective","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^total // {"headword":"total","category":"adjective","cefrLevel":"A1"}
Une situation où le gain total est fixé : ce qu'un joueur gagne, l'autre le perd.

Qu'est-ce que le minimax ?
^minimiser // {"headword":"minimiser","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"B2"}
^maximum // {"headword":"maximum","category":"other","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^une perte // {"headword":"perte","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^optimal // {"headword":"optimal","category":"adjective","cefrLevel":"B2"}
^un adversaire // {"headword":"adversaire","category":"noun","gender":"masculine","cefrLevel":"B1"}
Une stratégie visant à minimiser sa perte maximale possible en supposant que l'adversaire joue de façon optimale.

^the game // {"headword":"game","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"A1"}
# Game Theory

^the characteristic // {"headword":"characteristic","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B2"}
## Characteristics

What are the characteristics of game theory?
^the decision // {"headword":"decision","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^the player // {"headword":"player","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"A2"}
^the human // {"headword":"human","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"A1"}
^rational // {"headword":"rational","category":"adjective","cefrLevel":"B2"}
Decision theory, multiple players, considers the human as rational.

## Definitions

^the strategy // {"headword":"strategy","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B2"}
### Strategy

What is strategy not?
^the method // {"headword":"method","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B1"}
A method to be the smartest.

What is a strategy?
^the plan // {"headword":"plan","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"A2"}
^the behaviour // {"headword":"behaviour","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B2"}
^cover // {"headword":"cover","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^the case // {"headword":"case","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B2"}
A behaviour plan covering all cases.

^the sum // {"headword":"sum","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"A2"}
^zero // {"headword":"zero","category":"other","cefrLevel":"A1"}
### Zero-sum Game

What is a zero-sum game?
^the situation // {"headword":"situation","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^the gain // {"headword":"gain","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^lose // {"headword":"lose","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"A1"}
^win // {"headword":"win","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"A1"}
^fixed // {"headword":"fixed","category":"adjective","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^total // {"headword":"total","category":"adjective","cefrLevel":"A1"}
A situation where the total gain is fixed: what one player wins, the other loses.

What is minimax?
^minimize // {"headword":"minimize","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"B2"}
^maximum // {"headword":"maximum","category":"other","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^the loss // {"headword":"loss","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B2"}
^optimal // {"headword":"optimal","category":"adjective","cefrLevel":"C1"}
^the opponent // {"headword":"opponent","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B1"}
A strategy aiming to minimize one's maximum possible loss, assuming the opponent plays optimally.

^das Spiel // {"headword":"Spiel","category":"noun","gender":"neuter","cefrLevel":"A2"}
# Spieltheorie

^das Merkmal // {"headword":"Merkmal","category":"noun","gender":"neuter","cefrLevel":"B1"}
## Merkmale

Was sind die Merkmale der Spieltheorie?
^die Entscheidung // {"headword":"Entscheidung","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^der Spieler // {"headword":"Spieler","category":"noun","gender":"masculine","cefrLevel":"A2"}
^der Mensch // {"headword":"Mensch","category":"noun","gender":"masculine","cefrLevel":"A1"}
^rational // {"headword":"rational","category":"adjective","cefrLevel":"B2"}
Entscheidungstheorie, mehrere Spieler, betrachtet den Menschen als rational.

## Definitionen

^die Strategie // {"headword":"Strategie","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"B1"}
### Strategie

Was ist Strategie nicht?
^die Methode // {"headword":"Methode","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"B1"}
Eine Methode, um am intelligentesten zu sein.

Was ist eine Strategie?
^der Plan // {"headword":"Plan","category":"noun","gender":"masculine","cefrLevel":"A1"}
^das Verhalten // {"headword":"Verhalten","category":"noun","gender":"neuter","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^abdecken // {"headword":"abdecken","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"B2"}
^der Fall // {"headword":"Fall","category":"noun","gender":"masculine","cefrLevel":"A2"}
Ein Verhaltensplan, der alle Fälle abdeckt.

^die Summe // {"headword":"Summe","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"A1"}
^Null // {"headword":"Null","category":"other","cefrLevel":"A1"}
### Nullsummenspiel

Was ist ein Nullsummenspiel?
^die Situation // {"headword":"Situation","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"A2"}
^die Ausbeute // {"headword":"Ausbeute","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"B2"}
^verlieren // {"headword":"verlieren","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"A2"}
^gewinnen // {"headword":"gewinnen","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"A2"}
^festgelegt // {"headword":"festgelegt","category":"adjective","cefrLevel":"C1"}
^gesamt // {"headword":"gesamt","category":"adjective","cefrLevel":"B1"}
Eine Situation, in der die Gesamtausbeute festgelegt ist: Was ein Spieler gewinnt, verliert der andere.

Was ist das Minimax?
^minimieren // {"headword":"minimieren","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"B2"}
^maximal // {"headword":"maximal","category":"other","cefrLevel":"B2"}
^der Verlust // {"headword":"Verlust","category":"noun","gender":"masculine","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^optimal // {"headword":"optimal","category":"adjective","cefrLevel":"B2"}
^der Gegner // {"headword":"Gegner","category":"noun","gender":"masculine","cefrLevel":"B1"}
Eine Strategie, die darauf abzielt, den maximal möglichen Verlust zu minimieren, unter der Annahme, dass der Gegner optimal spielt.

^一场博弈 // {"headword":"博弈","category":"noun","classifier":"场","pinyin":"bó yì","cefrLevel":"C1"}
# 博弈论

^一个特点 // {"headword":"特点","category":"noun","classifier":"个","pinyin":"tè diǎn","cefrLevel":"B1"}
## 特点

博弈论的特点是什么？
^一个决策 // {"headword":"决策","category":"noun","classifier":"个","pinyin":"jué cè","cefrLevel":"B2"}
^一个玩家 // {"headword":"玩家","category":"noun","classifier":"个","pinyin":"wán jiā","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^一个人 // {"headword":"人","category":"noun","classifier":"个","pinyin":"rén","cefrLevel":"A1"}
^理性 // {"headword":"理性","category":"adjective","pinyin":"lǐ xìng","cefrLevel":"B2"}
决策理论，多人游戏，认为人类是理性的。

## 定义

^一个策略 // {"headword":"策略","category":"noun","classifier":"个","pinyin":"cè lüè","cefrLevel":"B2"}
### 策略

策略不是什么？
^一个方法 // {"headword":"方法","category":"noun","classifier":"个","pinyin":"fāng fǎ","cefrLevel":"B1"}
不是聪明绝顶的方法。

策略是什么？
^一个计划 // {"headword":"计划","category":"noun","classifier":"个","pinyin":"jì huà","cefrLevel":"A2"}
^一个行为 // {"headword":"行为","category":"noun","classifier":"个","pinyin":"xíng wéi","cefrLevel":"B2"}
^覆盖 // {"headword":"覆盖","category":"verb","pinyin":"fù gài","cefrLevel":"B2"}
^一种情况 // {"headword":"情况","category":"noun","classifier":"种","pinyin":"qíng kuàng","cefrLevel":"B1"}
是覆盖所有情况的行为计划。

^一个和 // {"headword":"和","category":"noun","classifier":"个","pinyin":"hé","cefrLevel":"A2"}
^零 // {"headword":"零","category":"other","cefrLevel":"A1","pinyin":"líng"}
### 零和游戏

什么是零和游戏？
^一种情况 // {"headword":"情况","category":"noun","classifier":"种","pinyin":"qíng kuàng","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^一个收益 // {"headword":"收益","category":"noun","classifier":"个","pinyin":"shōu yì","cefrLevel":"B2"}
^失去 // {"headword":"失去","category":"verb","pinyin":"shī qù","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^赢得 // {"headword":"赢得","category":"verb","pinyin":"yíng dé","cefrLevel":"B2"}
^固定 // {"headword":"固定","category":"adjective","pinyin":"gù dìng","cefrLevel":"B2"}
^总 // {"headword":"总","category":"adjective","pinyin":"zǒng","cefrLevel":"B1"}
总收益固定的情况：一个玩家赢得的，另一个失去。

什么是极小化极大？
^最小化 // {"headword":"最小化","category":"verb","pinyin":"zuì xiǎo huà","cefrLevel":"C1"}
^最大 // {"headword":"最大","category":"other","cefrLevel":"B1","pinyin":"zuì dà"}
^一个损失 // {"headword":"损失","category":"noun","classifier":"个","pinyin":"sǔn shī","cefrLevel":"B2"}
^最佳 // {"headword":"最佳","category":"adjective","pinyin":"zuì jiā","cefrLevel":"B2"}
^一个对手 // {"headword":"对手","category":"noun","classifier":"个","pinyin":"duì shǒu","cefrLevel":"B1"}
一种策略，旨在假设对手以最佳方式竞争情况下，最小化自己可能的最大损失。
